types of security problems: CIA
confidentiality, integrity, availability.

some issues are hard to catch and only occur under very specific conditions.

fork bomb - 1978

an algorithm that can detect all viruses can be proven to not exist.

may 13 1988 Jerusalem virus corrupted all executable files on infected machines.

1989 AIDS Trojan lies dormant for 90 boot cycles

2000 ILOVEYOU

2016 WannaCry

Ukraine power gird attack December 23, 2015 and December 17 2016

BLAST - Linux formal verification tool

this course is about analyzing software not monitoring networks or administrating networks.


